                  <desc>The word God is rubricated in the first three works; the word Mary is rubricated in the final two works
                  Columetric layout of text, <locus target="#103r #103v #104r #104v" facs="105 106 107"/> (Ps. 150), <locus target="#112v #113r #113v" facs="115 116"/> (tenth biblical canticle)</desc>
                  </handNote>
